<lb ed="I" n="0061a02"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><title>仇臣生造像記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<pb n="0062a" xml:id="I01.0024.0062a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0062a01"/><p cb:type="pre" xml:id="pI01p0062a0101">正光五年歲次甲辰七月己酉朔十五日<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0062001" n="0062001"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0062001" n="0062001"/><anchor xml:id="beg0062001" n="0062001"/>癸<anchor xml:id="end0062001"/>亥。
<lb ed="I" n="0062a02"/>雍州北地三原縣仇臣生。值遇上世。信心三寶。
<lb ed="I" n="0062a03"/>造石像一<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0062002" n="0062002"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0062002" n="0062002"/><anchor xml:id="beg0062002" n="0062002"/>區<anchor xml:id="end0062002"/>。上為皇帝陛下。州郡令長。七世父
<lb ed="I" n="0062a04"/>母。願上生天上。值遇諸佛。下隧人間。侯王長者
<lb ed="I" n="0062a05"/>之家。現世之報。延年益壽。子孫興隆。<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0062003" n="0062003"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0062003" n="0062003"/><anchor xml:id="beg0062003" n="0062003"/>所<anchor xml:id="end0062003"/>願如<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">斯</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0062a06"/>夫信欲稱善者。非至德不顯其功。欲游嵩岳者。
<lb ed="I" n="0062a07"/>非空寂<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0062004" n="0062004"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0062004" n="0062004"/><anchor xml:id="beg0062004" n="0062004"/>亦<anchor xml:id="end0062004"/>不達其<anchor xml:id="beg_1" type="star"/>所<anchor xml:id="end_1"/>。昔太子絕思於龍<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0062005" n="0062005"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0062005" n="0062005"/><anchor xml:id="beg0062005" n="0062005"/>華<anchor xml:id="end0062005"/>。身<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">體</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0062a08"/>如來之<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">願</unclear>。月<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">辰</unclear>叩白駒而脩禮。<anchor xml:id="beg_2" type="star"/>亦<anchor xml:id="end_2"/>蒙神道之助。
<lb ed="I" n="0062a09"/>是以積善成道。累<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0062006" n="0062006"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0062006" n="0062006"/><anchor xml:id="beg0062006" n="0062006"/>惡<anchor xml:id="end0062006"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0062007" n="0062007"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0062007" n="0062007"/><anchor xml:id="beg0062007" n="0062007"/>滅<anchor xml:id="end0062007"/>身。宜斑經藉。流芳來葉。
<lb ed="I" n="0062a10"/>不敢多進。　　親祖仇收　忘父仇進興
<lb ed="I" n="0062a11"/>　　　　　　　　　　　忘叔仇<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0062008" n="0062008"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0062008" n="0062008"/><anchor xml:id="beg0062008" n="0062008"/>歸<anchor xml:id="end0062008"/>興</p></cb:div>
</body>
